  <section id="about" class={initialPage === 'about' ? 'active' : ''}>
    <div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      <h2>Our <em>Story</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="about-intro">
      <p>Lumière began with a simple belief: a candle should do more than scent a room — it should slow you down. Every jar we pour is made in small batches at our studio in India, using 100% natural soya wax and botanically sourced fragrance oils.</p>
      <p>We never use paraffin, phthalates, or synthetic dyes. What you light is clean-burning, conscious, and designed to feel timeless — the kind of glow you reach for at the end of a long day.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-values">
      <div class="about-value-card">
        <h3>Natural Wax</h3>
        <p>Pure soya wax that burns evenly and slowly, releasing fragrance without petroleum byproducts or soot-heavy smoke.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-value-card">
        <h3>Small Batch</h3>
        <p>Each collection is hand-poured in limited runs. When a scent sells out, we restock thoughtfully — never at the cost of quality.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-value-card">
        <h3>Conscious Craft</h3>
        <p>Recyclable glass vessels, cotton wicks, and fragrances drawn from botanical sources. Minimal packaging, maximum intention.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-process">
      <div class="about-process-visual" id="aboutProcessVisual">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 280 360" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="220">
          <rect width="280" height="360" fill="#FFFBF0" rx="2"/>
          <rect x="70" y="140" width="140" height="170" rx="8" fill="#EDE5D8" stroke="#C4B5A0" stroke-width="1"/>
          <rect x="63" y="130" width="154" height="16" rx="4" fill="#E0D4C3" stroke="#C4B5A0" stroke-width="1"/>
          <line x1="140" y1="148" x2="140" y2="118" stroke="#8C7D6E" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <path d="M140 118 C132 106 130 92 140 82 C150 92 148 106 140 118Z" fill="#D4B07A" opacity="0.75"/>
          <path d="M140 115 C136 106 135 98 140 91 C145 98 144 106 140 115Z" fill="#F9EDD0"/>
          <text x="140" y="210" text-anchor="middle" font-family="'Cormorant Garamond', serif" font-size="10" fill="#2A2420" letter-spacing="2">HAND POURED</text>
          <text x="140" y="228" text-anchor="middle" font-family="'Jost', sans-serif" font-size="7" fill="#8C7D6E" letter-spacing="1.5">SOYA WAX</text>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="about-process-steps">
        <div class="about-step">
          <span class="about-step-num">01</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Source & Blend</h3>
            <p>Fragrance oils are blended in micro-batches and tested for throw, clarity, and burn performance before any pour.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-step">
          <span class="about-step-num">02</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Hand Pour</h3>
            <p>Wax is melted, tempered, and poured by hand into reusable glass jars with centered cotton wicks.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-step">
          <span class="about-step-num">03</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Cure & Ship</h3>
            <p>Candles cure for 48 hours, then are packed with recycled kraft wrap and shipped across India within 3–5 business days.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-quote">
      <blockquote>"We make candles for the in-between moments — when the day quiets and you need something warm, honest, and still."</blockquote>
      <cite>— The Lumière Studio</cite>
    </div>
  </section>

